  "informal_statement": "For every natural number n, twice the sum of 0, 1, ..., n equals n(n+1).",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Induction on n: base case sums to 0; step peels off the last term with `Finset.sum_range_succ`, applies the inductive hypothesis, and `ring` closes the arithmetic.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem gauss_sum (n : ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range (n + 1), i) * 2 = n * (n + 1)",
